com.google.api.client.json

Class JsonGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.json.JsonGenerator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndroidJsonGenerator, GsonGenerator, JacksonGenerator, JacksonGenerator, MockJsonGenerator

    public abstract class JsonGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract low-level JSON serializer.

    Implementation has no fields and therefore thread-safe, but sub-classes are not necessarily thread-safe.

    Upgrade warning: in prior version 1.13 there were methods writeNumber(UnsignedInteger) and writeNumber(UnsignedLong), but starting in version 1.14 they were removed. Instead use writeNumber(long) and writeNumber(BigInteger).

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    Yaniv Inbar
